1
00:00:18,410 --> 00:00:21,420
♪Wearing peach blossom makeup,
I boil tea over the stove♪

2
00:00:23,060 --> 00:00:25,780
♪With a pure heart,
I embroider the brocade of time♪

3
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,380
♪On the short paper,
affection flows in the silent moonlight♪

4
00:00:31,820 --> 00:00:34,940
♪I only wish that by my side,
is my love♪

5
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:39,940
♪Cool autumn wind blowing,
I gaze far leaning against the railing♪

6
00:00:41,620 --> 00:00:44,460
♪Sunset glow over the green hill,
in formation wild geese are flying♪

7
00:00:45,940 --> 00:00:50,020
♪Covering a thousand miles on horseback,
for whom is he longing♪

8
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:53,620
♪He returned home in dreams♪

9
00:00:54,060 --> 00:00:58,220
♪I will never forget
that you held my hands♪

10
00:00:58,740 --> 00:01:03,020
♪In your warm palms
and we braved winds and waves♪

11
00:01:03,380 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Unexpectedly, after we traveled so far
and turned grey-haired♪

12
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:11,660
♪I am still by your side♪

13
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:16,740
♪Hearts burning,
we look into each other's eyes♪

14
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:21,260
♪Feelings overflowing,
they don't need to be hided♪

15
00:01:21,820 --> 00:01:26,500
♪No matter how time passes
and life changes♪

16
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:30,860
♪Together, we will grow old♪

17
00:01:32,420 --> 00:01:36,380
=The Sword and the Brocade=

18
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:39,420
=Episode 28=

19
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,200
You donated so much money

20
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:48,920
just for this amulet.

21
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:50,560
I even think it's too much.

22
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:53,280
It'll work better when you donate more.

23
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,640
I'm sure

24
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,440
this amulet will make Yu

25
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,720
safe and happy.

26
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,000
Yu is lucky

27
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,000
to have a loving mother

28
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,520
like you.

29
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,000
Shiliu,

30
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,840
you are childless,
so you don't understand.

31
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,320
A child

32
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,960
is everything to his mother.

33
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,720
Whenever I think about

34
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,800
Yu,

35
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:13,800
I'd feel my life is full of hope.

36
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,560
Otherwise, we live in the back yard

37
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,720
and we seldom see His Lordship...

38
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:21,160
Shiliu,

39
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,520
I wasn't talking about you.

40
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:26,040
Please don't take it personally.

41
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:27,080
It's okay.

42
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,120
I know

43
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,560
you are a straightforward person.

44
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,320
I won't take it personally.

45
00:02:36,380 --> 00:02:36,940
(Xianling Pavilion)

46
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,200
Come and take a look.

47
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:40,960
We'll pass by Xianling Pavilion soon.

48
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:43,880
Maybe Her Ladyship is also there.

49
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,480
Shall we go there

50
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,520
and check if there's any trendy fabric

51
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,760
so that we can make new clothes?

52
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,000
But is it okay to go back home late?

53
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,000
We'll go there

54
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,240
and come back together
with Her Ladyship.

55
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,200
Great Madam won't blame us.

56
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:58,920
Come on.

57
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,480
The fabric, embroidery pattern

58
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,680
and stitches of this silk handkerchief

59
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,920
are exactly the same

60
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:17,960
as this piece of fabric

61
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,280
you kept.

62
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:21,440
Where did you

63
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,960
get this piece of silk?

64
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:24,920
I found it

65
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,960
from His Lordship's eldest son.

66
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:29,920
When

67
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:30,680
we checked

68
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,080
the records of the inventory,

69
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:35,120
Concubine Wen did asked

70
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,640
for this type of fabric before.

71
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:38,960
It's a match.

72
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,800
But people always say that
Marquis Yongping

73
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:43,880
is a righteous person.

74
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:47,480
Why would he kill innocent people?

75
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:48,960
That's right.

76
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,160
Even though what the coroner
and the hunter said

77
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,240
and this embroidery
directly point to him,

78
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:55,360
it's only collateral evidence.

79
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,680
We can't make

80
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,840
an arbitrary decision
that it's Marquis

81
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,960
who killed your mother just with this.

82
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,200
When he was drunk,

83
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,320
I asked him.

84
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,960
He said it was his fault

85
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,600
that my mother died.

86
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:21,360
But I still don't want to believe it.

87
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,920
I heard

88
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,080
the embroidery here

89
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,560
is the best in the capital.

90
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,200
I heard the same.

91
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,680
Madams,

92
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:34,000
what kind of embroidery do you want?

93
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:35,040
If we don't have it on display,

94
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,280
we can make customized products

95
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,600
for you.

96
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,040
Is Her Lady...

97
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:42,080
I mean, is Master Luo here?

98
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,800
Master Luo

99
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:46,000
is in the practice room right now.

100
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,320
Over there?

101
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,280
Yes. Please.

102
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:50,760
Thank you.

103
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,680
I don't believe His Lordship

104
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,160
would do such thing either.

105
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,320
Could it be

106
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,680
a misunderstanding?

107
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,440
I also hope it's a misunderstanding.

108
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:06,040
But the evidence is right here.

109
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,400
I...

110
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,040
If

111
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,760
it's all true,

112
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,400
then I...

113
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:53,000
I know you feel sad.

114
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:56,240
But it's not your fault.

115
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,800
It should be here.

116
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:14,640
This...

117
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:15,640
Wait.

118
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:16,160
This...

119
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,400
Didn't... Didn't you see that? That...

120
00:06:36,780 --> 00:06:39,580
(Virtue of Modesty and Patience)

121
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,920
Her Ladyship is not here?

122
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,000
My Lord.

123
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,960
Did Shiyi go
to Xianling Pavilion?

124
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,880
Her Ladyship didn't say.

125
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,520
She went out early in the morning.

126
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,120
What's with the lanterns?

127
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,320
My Lord,

128
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:08,200
Her Ladyship asked people

129
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:09,960
to take them down.

130
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,720
Why did you stop me?

131
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,000
Why can't we just confront Her Ladyship?

132
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,320
Lower your voice.

133
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,080
I can tell right away

134
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,640
that the man is Her Ladyship's lover.

135
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:38,720
Didn't you see that?

136
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:41,240
They were so close.

137
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,680
I was almost scared to death.

138
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,440
I don't think so.

139
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,880
Her Ladyship isn't that type of person.

140
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:47,360
She wouldn't do such thing

141
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:48,560
behind His Lordship's back.

142
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,800
Don't do anything recklessly

143
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,000
before you find out the truth.

144
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:53,160
You'd be in trouble if you caused chaos.

145
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,600
Then what kind of person she is?

146
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,880
She goes to Xianling Pavilion every day.

147
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:59,040
Is it really just for
teaching embroidery?

148
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,280
My Lord.

149
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:10,160
Oh, no.

150
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,840
I was talking loud.

151
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,040
Did His Lordship hear me?

152
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,240
I'm sure he did.

153
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:14,920
He must be

154
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,520
on his way to Xianling Pavilion now.

155
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,960
It's bad. It's so bad.

156
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,520
Would he get mad at me

157
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,920
because of what I said?

158
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,520
He doesn't have time

159
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,800
to be mad at you right now.

160
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,840
Hope nothing will happen
to Xianling Pavilion.

161
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,440
Let's go and take a look.

162
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,720
Come on. Let's go.

163
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:29,680
But...

164
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:32,440
If your mother was really
killed by His Lordship,

165
00:08:32,790 --> 00:08:34,320
what should we do?

166
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,960
The details still remain unclear.

167
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:43,000
We'd better investigate it carefully.

168
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,120
Then how should we investigate it?

169
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,720
Let me take a walk first.

170
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:55,920
Be careful.

171
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:00,520
Shiyi.

172
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,240
Go home with me.

173
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,560
Go home with me.

174
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:19,480
You need to ask for her opinion first.

175
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:22,320
Who are you?

176
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,920
I'm Shiyi's friend.

177
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,240
If she doesn't want to go,

178
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:26,520
you can't force her to.

179
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:32,720
My Lord,

180
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:33,840
I just remembered.

181
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,800
He's Ou Yanxing,
the second son of the Ou family.

182
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:39,920
What's your purpose

183
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:41,040
of approaching my wife?

184
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,200
Has your Ou family become

185
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,200
shameless like this?

186
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,240
There's nothing between Shiyi and me.

187
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:48,320
How dare you call her Shiyi?

188
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,240
My Lord.

189
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:50,560
Mr. Ou isn't the type of person

190
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,640
you think he is.

191
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,040
Mr. Ou?

192
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:55,520
So you knew that
he's one of the Ou family

193
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:56,760
and you were still seeing him?

194
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:01,560
Stop fighting.

195
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:05,800
Xu Lingyi.

196
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:09,800
Shiyi.

197
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,080
It's dangerous. Put down the scissors.

198
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,960
You really don't care about
people's lives?

199
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,240
You are actually threatening me

200
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:26,040
with your own life for him?

201
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:29,120
Put down the scissors.

202
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,440
Put down the sword.

203
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:22,400
My Lord.

204
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:24,880
My Lord.

205
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:26,360
My Lord.

206
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,880
Your Ladyship. What have you done?

207
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,360
My Lord.

208
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:41,040
Linbo.

209
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:43,920
Let's go.

210
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:49,560
-My Lord.
-My Lord.

211
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:50,880
My Lord.

212
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:51,280
Oh, gosh.

213
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,600
How did you get hurt?

214
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:54,400
-A lot of blood.
-My Lord.

215
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,800
Take His Lordship back.

216
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,480
Your Ladyship, is it you?

217
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:04,200
Is it you who stabbed His Lordship?

218
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:05,760
Why did you do that?

219
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:07,480
Just say someone tried to assassinate
me outside of the capital.

220
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,160
What happened here today

221
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:11,000
must be kept a secret.

222
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:12,200
Otherwise, you'll

223
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,240
all be expelled from the Xu family.

224
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:16,600
Let's go.

225
00:12:17,280 --> 00:12:18,960
His Lordship still needs to
go to Shandong in a couple of days.

226
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,240
Stop talking.

227
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:21,800
Let's go.

228
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,440
My Lord.

229
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:08,520
Great Madam.

230
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,320
What happened?

231
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:11,560
Tell me.

232
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:13,400
We

233
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,200
encountered assassins
outside of the capital.

234
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,280
Assassins?

235
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:19,160
You are his Vice General.

236
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:20,880
How did you fail in protecting him?

237
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,000
Oh, no.

238
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:26,480
It's a lot of blood.

239
00:13:26,760 --> 00:13:28,640
How badly he must have wounded.

240
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:29,520
Mother.

241
00:13:29,680 --> 00:13:31,160
We have to report this.

242
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:32,840
According to the imperial edict,

243
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,720
His Lordship will have to
leave for Shandong in three days.

244
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,560
If we don't report this accident,

245
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:37,680
and he can't leave in three days,

246
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,040
he'll be punished
for defying the imperial edict.

247
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:40,360
That makes sense.

248
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,880
Kuan'er, go, now.

249
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:45,160
Yes, Mother.

250
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:46,400
Don't go.

251
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:48,160
Do not report this.

252
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:06,160
The wound is quite deep.

253
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:11,240
Lingyi.

254
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:12,120
Mother.

255
00:14:12,800 --> 00:14:13,800
How did...

256
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:16,800
How did you get hurt?

257
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:20,200
Tell me.

258
00:14:20,640 --> 00:14:22,640
Why can't we report this?

259
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:25,120
With your condition,

260
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:27,040
how can you go to Shandong?

261
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:28,800
If we don't report this,

262
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:31,800
how can we explain to His Majesty?

263
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,560
Defying the imperial edict

264
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:36,560
is a capital offense.

265
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:37,640
Lingyi,

266
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:39,160
you'll get yourself killed.

267
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,520
I have my reasons.

268
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:45,880
Do as I say.

269
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:48,400
Mother,

270
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:50,840
promise me.

271
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:54,520
Alright.

272
00:14:55,680 --> 00:14:57,040
I'll listen to you.

273
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:58,840
I promise.

274
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:07,520
Physician, please
treat Lingyi carefully.

275
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:11,440
His Lordship needs rest.

276
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:12,520
Everybody,

277
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:15,440
please leave and let him rest.

278
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:16,880
Okay.

279
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:19,240
Lingyi needs rest.

280
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:21,360
Let's go back.

281
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:18,080
This thing is quite strange.

282
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:20,320
Lingyi wouldn't tell me the truth.

283
00:16:20,680 --> 00:16:23,840
But I know he's hiding
something from me.

284
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:26,160
Now, get someone

285
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,640
to investigate this thing

286
