00:47:46,400 --> 00:47:48,200
-Put out the fire.
-Hurry. Over there. Hurry.

850
00:47:48,400 --> 00:47:48,800
Let's go first.

851
00:47:50,440 --> 00:47:51,320
This way. This way.

852
00:47:53,000 --> 00:47:53,440
My Lord.

853
00:47:53,640 --> 00:47:54,760
Is your wound open again?

854
00:47:54,960 --> 00:47:55,440
No.

855
00:47:56,600 --> 00:47:57,520
The fire is too strong.

856
00:47:57,720 --> 00:47:58,320
Call help.

857
00:47:58,520 --> 00:47:59,600
But with your condition...

858
00:47:59,920 --> 00:48:00,560
I'm fine.

859
00:48:00,760 --> 00:48:02,280
I've given an order. Go.

860
00:48:02,320 --> 00:48:03,240
Water. Water.

861
00:48:03,360 --> 00:48:04,040
Yes.

862
00:48:04,240 --> 00:48:05,000
Hurry.

863
00:48:08,640 --> 00:48:09,320
Water is here.

864
00:48:09,680 --> 00:48:10,480
Not enough.

865
00:48:10,600 --> 00:48:11,640
Hurry. Hurry. Hurry.

866
00:48:26,780 --> 00:48:30,500
♪In the cold darkness of midnight,
a sigh is heard♪

867
00:48:30,580 --> 00:48:33,500
♪Who picked up the paintbrush
to draw loneliness♪

868
00:48:34,660 --> 00:48:41,060
♪In my life, I can draw everything,
but lovesickness♪

869
00:48:41,300 --> 00:48:44,220
♪The mountain city is waiting for rain♪

870
00:48:45,020 --> 00:48:48,540
♪I am waiting for you
to pass in my memory♪

871
00:48:49,100 --> 00:48:54,380
♪The sky is in a more lonely color
than your face♪

872
00:48:55,260 --> 00:48:58,540
♪The wind rises
and the candle light flickers♪

873
00:48:59,220 --> 00:49:01,700
♪The thin clothes
can't stand the cold days♪

874
00:49:02,940 --> 00:49:09,820
♪Full of twists and turns,
fate is untold♪

875
00:49:10,060 --> 00:49:12,660
♪I ground my thoughts into ink♪

876
00:49:13,020 --> 00:49:16,860
♪But I still can't sketch your contours♪

877
00:49:17,180 --> 00:49:22,460
♪How could the ink
and paper exhaust our stories♪

878
00:49:23,700 --> 00:49:29,660
♪Who picked up the pen
to disturb the heart♪

879
00:49:30,500 --> 00:49:37,460
♪Who visited to remind me of the past♪

880
00:49:38,060 --> 00:49:41,900
♪If feelings can be kept in mind,
but cannot be confessed♪

881
00:49:42,460 --> 00:49:45,500
♪I won't escape from whatever end♪

882
00:49:45,900 --> 00:49:51,180
♪In the dim lantern light,
with you there is me♪

883
00:49:51,700 --> 00:49:58,100
♪Who picked up the pen
to set free lonely tears♪

884
00:49:58,900 --> 00:50:05,140
♪Whoever visited my life,
only you stayed all the days♪

885
00:50:05,660 --> 00:50:10,100
♪If the moth doesn't fly into the fire♪

886
00:50:10,380 --> 00:50:13,900
♪How can it be said to be persistent♪

887
00:50:14,220 --> 00:50:19,820
♪Coming to the end of your story,
there is me♪
